description:
The world changed because one girl lost the one dearest to her. The grief-stricken girl kept searching for a way to bring him back to her, eventually became a scientist, creating a substance that looked to have promising results.

That substance was &lsquo;Metaphysic particles&rsquo; which could transform mankind&rsquo;s wildest dreams into reality, wondrous particles that could smash the divide between the spirit and the being.

But a grave error occurred in the research before it reached completion, and the Metaphysic particles were spread throughout the world. Incredible occurrences were happening throughout the world.

&lsquo;Monsters&rsquo; which preyed on humans appeared, recognized by the masses to be a consequence of the Metaphysic particles. It appeared to them to be the girl&rsquo;s fault, and they ostracized her, calling her &lsquo;The Witch&rsquo;.

But from the masses emerged people who could use the Metaphysic particles to do battle with the monsters, Knights of Justice who transformed their beliefs into magical creatures to defeat the monsters. Using the twelve devices &lsquo;Accessories&rsquo; that could magnify these beliefs, they became known as &lsquo;12&rsquo;

This is a story of a world where dreams become reality&hellip;

&quot;Love Flower&quot;
A three-part story featuring a loving adult couple who find a high school girl devastated by her senpai's apparent rejection of her feelings. The two women encourage her, and happily watch as a romance very reminiscent of their own teenage years begins to develop.

&quot;Romance Women's Detective File&quot;

&quot;Milky Way of the Two&quot;

&quot;Mystery of the President&quot;

This world is an ocean of &quot;whispers.&quot;

Kouji is a lethargic high school student who walks aimlessly through life. One day, he stumbles upon a young boy sleeping beneath a tree. On either side of the boy are a dog and a cat, all three bathed in the broken sunlight streaming through the leaves above. 

Before long, Kouji comes to realize that this boy, Daichi, is like him. Both possess the ability to hear the voices of objects and animals. Well, possess[b]ed[/b], in Kouji's case. Kouji lost his powers long ago &ndash; or so he thinks&hellip;

&quot;Tomorrow, I'll put a curse on my father&hellip;&quot;

Right after reuniting with his father, from whom he'd been separated as a child, Ryou suddenly traveled back in time 22 years, during the peak of the bubble economy of the Showa era!

There, he met his father, Konomi, who was 3 years younger than he was&hellip;!

Living in an unknown environment with the uneasiness of wanting to go back to his own time, Ryou was anxious. But being comforted by the pure-hearted Konomi, his feelings gradually started to change&hellip;

